---
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
title: "About"
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full bg-black text-white overflow-hidden font-serif">
  <!-- Background -->
  <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Mystical Forest" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0" />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-purple-800/40 to-black/90 z-10 backdrop-blur-md"></div>

  <!-- Animated Particles -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none starfield mix-blend-screen"></div>

  <!-- Foreground Content -->
  <div class="relative z-30 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-yellow-100 drop-shadow-glow mb-8 animate-fade-in">
      ❈ Enter the World of <span class="text-pink-300">Fishnini</span> ❈
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-purple-200 leading-relaxed mb-12 animate-slide-up">
      Beyond time and beyond memory — here, you are reborn. Foxes ink your dreams, stars murmur your forgotten name, and moonlit rivers remember where you’ve been.
    </p>

    <!-- Floating Scroll -->
    <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-white/5 to-white/10 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-fairy max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-glow-in">
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        ✦ Every whisper in the glade belongs to you.<br />
        ✦ The wind is your past life’s lullaby.<br />
        ✦ The forest didn’t find you — it remembered you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a href="#top" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-400 via-purple-500 to-amber-300 text-black font-semibold px-10 py-3 rounded-full shadow-md hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
        ✧ Back to Top ✧
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes slide-up {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes glow-in {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); filter: blur(4px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0); }
}

.animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 1s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1.2s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-glow-in { animation: glow-in 1.6s ease-out forwards; }

.starfield {
  background-image: radial-gradient(white 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 24px 24px;
  animation: twinkle 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  opacity: 0.05;
}
@keyframes twinkle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.04; }
  50% { opacity: 0.10; }
}

.drop-shadow-glow {
  text-shadow: 0 0 8px #facc15, 0 0 18px #f472b6;
}
.shadow-fairy {
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08),
              0 0 40px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.12),
              0 0 60px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.16);
}

h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
}
p {
  font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
}
</style>

